Summary: Large triangular object with three intensely bright white lights.
divs: Sighting DetailsSubject viewed this object at approximately 6:25 PM EST, just hanging there, motionless, about 100 ft. over the Main Street Bridge, with no blinking lights, which one would expect to observe with an airplane, or helicopter. I sat at a light on a suburban downtown street, with only moderate traffic, but when I put the window down, there was no audible sound. Mind you, I was on a street in the downtown, but this is not a big city, and I would have easily been able to hear if it was a helicopter, or airplane. Plus, there's no airport nearby. I decided to investigate farther, and I went around the block, but by then, the object was nowhere to be seen.
